And don't forget the report with pics!

I remember heading out my December 27th what ever year. It was for one of the first fire hall ones. My wife thought I was. Nuts driving 2.5 hours to just have wings with guys and girls I only knew on line.  I'm glad I made the trip As I firmed up life. Long friends.
Hope everyone made it home safe last night, I think we had about 10 or so people show up and hang out till about 10! Good time was had and it was a pleasure to make the acquaintance of everyone there
What? No camera? Glad you all had a good time.
Forgot to bring the camera. Good to see smiling faces, both old and new. They even got Spiel out of his cave.
LOL

I appreciated the opportunity to meet some of the members here last night. I thought that this would be a worth wile forum to join and I was proven right. Thanks guys and I look forward to seeing you and others as the seasons pass.  Jim
